    {
      "parameters": {
        "promptType": "define",
        "text": "=You are a feedback classification engine. Analyze the following customer feedback and return ONLY a valid JSON object — no explanation, no markdown, no extra text.\n\nClassify into EXACTLY one of these categories:\n- Complaint\n- Compliment\n- Query\n- Feature Request\n- Other\n\nAlso provide:\n- sentiment: a score from -1.0 (very negative) to 1.0 (very positive)\n- priority: \"High\", \"Medium\", or \"Low\" (High = urgent complaint or critical bug, Medium = general complaint or feature request, Low = compliment or general query)\n- summary: a one-sentence summary of the feedback (max 20 words)\n\nRespond ONLY with this JSON structure:\n{\n  \"category\": \"<one of the five categories above>\",\n  \"sentiment\": <float between -1.0 and 1.0>,\n  \"priority\": \"<High|Medium|Low>\",\n  \"summary\": \"<one sentence summary>\"\n}\n\nFeedback: {{ $json.Feedback }}",
        "options": {}
      },
      "type": "@n8n/n8n-nodes-langchain.agent",
      "typeVersion": 3.1,
      "position": [
